## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="1e6f8-102">Пользовательские синтеза речи определить типы событий, отправляемых на инфраструктуре платформы синтезатора речи с <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1e6f8-102">Custom speech synthesis engines define the types of events submitted to the Speech platform synthesizer infrastructure with the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="1e6f8-103">Спецификация выполняется путем задания <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo.EventId%2A> свойство <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo> передаваемый экземпляров <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.AddEvents%2A> член класса, реализующего <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite> передается интерфейс <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A> метод механизма пользовательских речи Реализация <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1e6f8-103">Specification is performed by setting the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo.EventId%2A> property of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo> instances passed to the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.AddEvents%2A> member of the class implementing the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite> interface passed to the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A> method on a custom speech engine's implementation of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="1e6f8-104">Инфраструктуре платформы обработки речи указывает тип события, обрабатываемого в данный момент через <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> свойство <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite> передаваемый speak реализации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1e6f8-104">The Speech platform infrastructure indicates the type of events it is currently handling through the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> property on the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite> passed to the speak implementation.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="1e6f8-105">Значение <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> Битовая маска, где члены <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId> определяют расположение бита, в соответствии с типом события.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1e6f8-105">The value of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> is a bitmask, where the members of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId> define the location of the bit corresponding to the event type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1e6f8-106">Например, WordBoundary имеет пять (5), то есть пятый бит в значение, возвращаемое значение <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> указывает, поддерживает ли узел типа события.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1e6f8-106">For example, WordBoundary has a value of five (5), meaning the fifth bit in the value returned by <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> indicates if the site supports the event type.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="1e6f8-107">Ниже приведен пример часть реализации синтеза речи пользовательских наследование от <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>и с помощью использование <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState>, и <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1e6f8-107">The example below is part of a custom speech synthesis implementation inheriting from <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>, and using the use of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState>, and <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId></span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="1e6f8-108">Реализация <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1e6f8-108">The implementation of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A></span></span>  
  
1.  <span data-ttu-id="1e6f8-109">Получает массив <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> экземпляров и создает новый массив <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> экземпляры должны быть переданы `Speak` метода для базового механизма синтеза.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1e6f8-109">Receives an array of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> instances and creates a new array of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> instances to be passed to the `Speak` method on an underlying synthesis engine.</span></span>  
  
2.  <span data-ttu-id="1e6f8-110">Если <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction> , найдено значение перечисления из <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState.Action%2A> свойство <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState.Action%2A> возвращенных <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A> каждого экземпляра <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A> экземпляр <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction>, реализация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1e6f8-110">If the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction> enumeration value by found from the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState.Action%2A> property on the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState.Action%2A> returned by the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A> property of each <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.State%2A> instance is <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction>, the implementation</span></span>  
  
    -   <span data-ttu-id="1e6f8-111">Преобразует Americanism для Britishisms в Произносимый текст.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1e6f8-111">Translates Americanism to Britishisms in the text to be spoken.</span></span>  
  
    -   <span data-ttu-id="1e6f8-112">Если <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> свойство <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> интерфейсов, предоставляемых для реализации поддержки типом события WordBoundary <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo> позволяет создать событие для диска индикатор синтезатора создается экземпляр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1e6f8-112">If the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> property on the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> interfaces provided to the implementation support the WordBoundary event type, a <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo> instance is used to create an event to drive a synthesizer progress meter is created.</span></span>  
  
3.  <span data-ttu-id="1e6f8-113">Затем вызывается механизм визуализации речи с измененной <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> массива.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1e6f8-113">A speech rendering engine is then called with the modified <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> array.</span></span>  
  
```  
private const int WordBoundaryFlag = 1 << (int)TtsEventId.WordBoundary;  
private readonly char[] spaces = new char[] { ' ', '\t', '\r', '\n' };  
internal struct UsVsUk  
{  
  internal string UK;  
  internal string US;  
}  
  
override public void Speak (TextFragment [] frags, IntPtr wfx, ITtsEngineSite site)  
{  
  TextFragment [] newFrags=new TextFragment[frags.Length];  
  
  for (int i=0;i<frags.Length;i++){  
    newFrags[i].State=frags[i].State;  
    //truncate  
    newFrags[i].TextToSpeak = frags[i].TextToSpeak.Substring(frags[i].TextOffset,  
                               frags[i].TextLength);  
    newFrags[i].TextLength = newFrags[i].TextToSpeak.Length;  
    newFrags[i].TextOffset = 0;  
    if (newFrags[i].State.Action == TtsEngineAction.Speak) {  
      //Us to UK conversion  
      foreach (UsVsUk term in TransList) {  
      newFrags[i].TextToSpeak.Replace(term.US, term.UK);  
      }  
      //Generate progress meter events if supported  
      if ((site.EventInterest & WordBoundaryFlag) != 0) {  
      string[] subs = newFrags[i].TextToSpeak.Split(spaces);  
  
      foreach (string s in subs) {  
        int offset = newFrags[i].TextOffset;  
        SpeechEventInfo spEvent = new SpeechEventInfo((Int16)TtsEventId.WordBoundary,   
                (Int16)EventParameterType.Undefined,   
                 s.Length, new IntPtr(offset));  
        offset += s.Length;  
        if (s.Trim().Length > 0) {  
          SpeechEventInfo[] events = new SpeechEventInfo[1];  
          events[0] = spEvent;  
          site.AddEvents(events, 1);  
        }  
      }  
      }  
    }  
  }  
  
  _baseSynthesize.Speak(newFrags, wfx, site);  
  
}  
```
